\item \label{exer:EulersThm} Distinguish the case of two vertices. andanswers.texhas an enumerated list with this,
\item \label{ans:EulersThm} There is no Euler path, except if there
are exactly two vertices. After compiling the exercises, hints, and answers documents, entering this in the body
oflectures.texwill result in the lectures getting the reference numbers used in the other
documents.

